  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    The Application class describes a complete MVC application.
    Controller<M extends Model,V extends View>
    The Controller class describes all the basic functionality of a controller within the MVC architecture.
    Model
    The Model class describes all the basic functionality of a model within the MVC architecture.
    Radio<T>
    The Radio class describes an event emitter that can be used for emitting and listening to events.
    View<M extends Model,C extends Controller>
    The View class describes all the basic functionality of a view within the MVC architecture.
